{
  "texts": [
    "We estimate concrete security of the FHE parameter sets given in Section 5.",
    "1 using the open-source Lattice Estimator tool [APS15a].",
    "The Lattice Estimator is widely used in estimating the security of FHE parameter sets [ACC + 19] as well as more broadly in lattice-based cryptography.",
    "Algorithms for solving LWE, that are currently supported in the Lattice Estimator, include the primal attack [BG14, ADPS16], the dual attack [MR09, Alb17, GJ21, MAT22], decoding attacks [LN13], Coded-BKW [GJS15, KF15], and algebraic algorithms [AG11, ACF + 15].",
    "Some combinatorial algorithms, including hybrid combinatorial and lattice algorithms [How07, ACW19, CHHS19, EJK20] are also supported."
  ]
}